data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite single-family residence boasts four spacious bedrooms and two beautifully appointed baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. The attached two-car garage ensures convenience and plenty of storage. Situated in a charming neighborhood with NO HOA, you'll enjoy the freedom to personalize and customize your space to your heart's content. The recently updated kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring modern amenities and sleek finishes. Take advantage of the built-in wine cooler, perfect for entertaining and showcasing your finest vintages. Natural light floods the interior, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. The open floor plan provides a seamless flow between living spaces, making it an ideal setting for gatherings and quality family time. Step outside to the covered patio, offering a serene retreat for alfresco dining or simply basking in the fresh air. Escape to your own private oasis in the backyard, complete with an above-ground pool that comes with the house. Whether you're looking to cool off on a hot summer day or host unforgettable poolside gatherings, this feature is sure to be a hit. This residence strikes the perfect balance between functionality and luxury, offering a blend of comfort and style. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the magic for yourself!
